## Parity config
This directory contains the parity node config

To get a valid config you need to combine

- base.toml

with one of the role configs

- observer-role.toml
- participant-role.toml
- validator-role.toml

and one of the chain specific configs

- ../laika/config.toml
- ../tlbc/config.toml

Because the config files will just be concatenated, this only works with
disjoint parity configs.
